# This is to be used more as a reference than anything. Just a list of files that I like to have installed with brew on Mac
# at the bottom, the command for installing brew itself, and the commands to install everything at once
# brew

ack
babl
coreutils
ffmpeg
findutils
gawk
grep
lame
libav
neovim
moreutils
node
